{"tid":2070433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：成立獨立調查委員會唯一目的係報仇！","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:19:05.000Z","uid":7542,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d85d96b859d7425fba3012b6d23577194ebbcacb","tid":2070433,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">BINGO！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於不少聲音要求成立的獨立調查委員會，林鄭月娥當時以加入兩名新監警會成員作回應，葉劉淑儀指除非有人想尋仇，「他踢我一腳，我要踢回他、要罰他」，否則不認為要成立獨立調查委員會。一直主張成立獨立調查委員會調查整件社會事件的張炳良指，監警會沒足夠法定的調查權力，而不論任何一個政府部門，包括警隊在內都不會希望被人調查，但他認為政府不應只考慮單獨部門的利益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532953-20200619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532953-20200619.htm&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=8b2a9d36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532953-20200619.htm&h=c1148a4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532953-20200619.htm</a>"},{"pid":"af6c00f36311adedc1decfd4b09da8e6352f483e","tid":2070433,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=23b2acf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"e476c60ce7067b14a7fa7902fb3bb832fcf51b33","tid":2070433,"uid":73340,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"尋咩仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係清白既邊會有事發生"},{"pid":"c3dee9f9b79eed9e8e12bcc2a5bdcec3f3b6c899","tid":2070433,"uid":85327,"like":1,"dislike"